on pre-filter captures larger debris, such as dust and hair. This filter also prolongs the life of your HEPA filter, preventing these larger elements from clogging it. The HEPA filter is designed to capture the smallest particles, ranging from relatively large pollen particulates to extremely small smoke particles. The machine does not include the extra cleaning stage of an ionizer. However, many prefer purifiers without this feature, as it emits trace amounts of ozone.","The Idylis AC-2118 includes an auto mode, a convenient feature that senses the ambient air quality in your home and adjusts its settings to maximize its cleaning effectiveness. The machine also includes a sleep mode that dims the panel lights and sets the fan speed on its low setting so as not to disturb you at night. This mode cleans the air without making a lot of noise and also conserves energy as a nice side effect of running on minimal settings."]},"id":"3abe4328-6918-4dcc-bde0-7e22e638583d","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Convenience"},"id":"e90d9987-192c-4899-8bf4-2aaf6d823194","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/aaE353fAdauVnJibJCAAQC.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Perhaps reflecting its ability to clean large rooms, this Idylis air cleaner is among the largest machines we reviewed. It weighs nearly 19 pounds, so it isn&#39;t the heaviest purifier we found but is still quite hefty compared to some. Storing it can be a little tricky, as it is the tallest and deepest machine we reviewed at nearly 30 inches tall and 13 inches deep. You&#39;ll want to dedicate some closet or storage space for this machine when you don&#39;t want to run it. Unfortunately, this air cleaner lacks handles to help you move it around the house as you need.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56398-idylis-iap-1010.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/aaE353fAdauVnJibJCAAQC.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"aaE353fAdauVnJibJCAAQC","mos":"http